#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"One option `(1)` for doing a full GC would be when it estimates that the "
"used heap will exceed maximum heap size,\n"
"but that wasn’t our case.\n"
"The other `(2)` would be if enough minimal collections had happened and the "
"used heap was above the minimum heap size.\n"
"This latter option was what was happening here."
